- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper may involve image analysis of medical scans.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a less likely category, but possible as the paper proposes an AI-based decision support tool for physicians.
